                            <comment id="17310203" author="davsclaus" created="Sun, 28 Mar 2021 13:28:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Try with Camel 3.9.0 where we have fixed and improved the kafka component.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17312138" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 07:20:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah I looked in the code, and yes we should make camel-kafka commit accordingly to the autoCommitOnStop configuration option.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reproting.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17312330" author="suneetk92" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 12:49:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, it was still causing issue in 3.9.0.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I was trying to fix it, but seems like you have already fixed it.&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you mind sharing the Pull Request id?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17312361" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 12:54:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/73c674b54df5ff741939629abd4564583f98c199&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/73c674b54df5ff741939629abd4564583f98c199&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/f9b1a3da477ccb3989bc67f6aa8a10f344d6321a&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/commit/f9b1a3da477ccb3989bc67f6aa8a10f344d6321a&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17312365" author="suneetk92" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 13:02:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here, it is checking both isStoppingOrStopped() and isSuspendingOrSuspended()&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/73c674b54df5ff741939629abd4564583f98c199/components/camel-kafka/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/kafka/KafkaConsumer.java#L339&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/73c674b54df5ff741939629abd4564583f98c199/components/camel-kafka/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/kafka/KafkaConsumer.java#L339&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, shouldn&apos;t &lt;br/&gt;
 boolean stopping = isStoppingOrStopped() || isSuspendingOrSuspended();&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17312369" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 13:09:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yeah its actually better to check for !isRunAllowed so I am doing a new commit for that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
